  ID: MalteseSoldier
  Name: Elderly Maltese conscript
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: 'He hauled grain his whole life and never once touched a sword. When
    the wall gave way under bombardment, stone slammed his pelvis sideways. He cannot
    move his legs; he stares at the sky.


    Treatment: No tourniquet helps. No
    splint reaches the fracture. You give him water and cloth for comfort. If someone
    chooses the dagger, that is not your hand.'
